{"tid":1826661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成日話靜咗，根本冇靜過，只係戰場唔同咗，自己睇西區議會咩事","createTime":"2020-01-16T10:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T13:27:03.000Z","uid":79724,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e6e9904e1ce8d7f78ddae491796d5cd0b4351723","tid":1826661,"uid":79724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T10:06:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YqzDSeV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYqzDSeV.jpg&h=c4f3251d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n片<br />\n<a href=\"https://fbwat.ch/1DR4JGq7Flxd1c1t\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffbwat.ch%2F1DR4JGq7Flxd1c1t&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GLM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=1a9e4a94\" target=\"_blank\">https://fbwat.ch/1DR4JGq7Flxd1c1t</a><br />\n<br />\n鄧仆街拉班狗離場就意料中事，政府因立場唔同就可以疏忽職守走人，仲話以後唔嚟？份人工嘔返出嚟唔該。<br />\n<br />\n文宣方向建議：<br />\n<br />\n好多淺黃對區議會寄予厚望，而家港共擺明玩架空。<span style=\"color: green;\">我希望思想比較前嘅手足忍下口，唔好笑佢哋，一嚟係自己人係手足，二嚟而家佢哋對體制幻滅，將來只會並肩行得更前。請大家因勢利導，要啟蒙手足，而唔係笑走、鬧走佢哋。</span><br />\n<br />\n我明好多人好心急，好不滿好多人好似放棄咗街頭戰線咁。事實係體制內外任何能夠做嘅，都要做到盡。<span style=\"color: green;\">一定要相信自己，相信香港人。</span>"},{"pid":"489d0fdb2f14245a027a919855a1cce3d5981944","tid":1826661,"uid":79724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T10:56:39.000Z","msg":"留負皮嘅出嚟講下點解啦"},{"pid":"22c1d5d3e057d2420d778b06d3644e0bc4d54ef4","tid":1826661,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T11:07:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f92ea18f569dddaa909ff29f3539b751d6cd4c6d","tid":1826661,"uid":162008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T11:23:02.000Z","msg":"唔岩立場就搵大隊走人，已經塞哂兩邊耳仔，又話聆聽？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台灣就公投完啦 咁香港人呢？<br />\n<br />\n香港人唔可以再慣性沉默，一起發聲，習慣投票表達意見吧<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票<br />\n一個香港人的投票應用程式<br />\n<br />\n下載連結：iOS / Android<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkvote.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkvote.org&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GLM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=64829ea6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkvote.org</a>"},{"pid":"677ea918ab8b859fbac93fc29bb0a5c9d8620413","tid":1826661,"uid":79724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T13:27:03.000Z","msg":"推"}]}